      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>spinach</strong> to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> under the cold tap until it's cool</p><p>Once cool, squeeze the water out of the spinach as much as you can</p><p>Boil the kettle again (last time, we promise!)</p>",
