      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter alternative</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk alternative</strong></p><p>Mash until smooth, then add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>spinach</strong></p><p>Stir in the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>cheddar flavour block</strong> and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong> and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>cheezy spinach mash</strong></p>",
