      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoked basa</strong> over the<strong> cheezy spinach mash </strong>and<strong> </strong>top with a<strong> poached egg</strong> and a generous crack of black <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
